        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Physics Suppose that during a storm, the force of the wind blowing against a Skyscraper can be expressed by the vector (115, 2018, 0), where each measure in the ordered triple represents the force in Newtons. What is the magnitude of this force? (Lesson 8-3)",
